64
00:04:22.862 --> 00:04:23.730  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Nagai!

65
00:04:24.264 --> 00:04:25.598  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
