68
00:04:37.677 --> 00:04:38.811  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yeah.

69
00:04:40.380 --> 00:04:41.281  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
