95
00:06:02.862 --> 00:06:03.763  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Mr. Sato!

96
00:06:03.830 --> 00:06:04.964  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
