105
00:06:40.867 --> 00:06:43.069  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[explosion nearby then all shouting]

106
00:06:49.442 --> 00:06:51.511  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
