to drive the threat home, right?

107
00:06:51.577 --> 00:06:52.445  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
No.

108
00:06:52.745 --> 00:06:55.114  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I never heard anything
about actually firing these...

109
00:06:55.748 --> 00:06:57.083  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What's going on?

110
00:06:58.985 --> 00:07:00.520  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Wh-- What is this?

111
00:07:03.623 --> 00:07:06.659  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
