-Hurry, get a damage report!

113
00:07:10.930 --> 00:07:12.832  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Have security check the defensive walls!

114
00:07:14.534 --> 00:07:16.569  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Sato] <i>Colonel Kouma, right?</i>

115
00:07:17.603 --> 00:07:20.873  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
