conventional like that.

116
00:07:21.140 --> 00:07:25.077  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What I want is this entire country.

117
00:07:28.981 --> 00:07:31.150  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>This is your final warning.</i>

118
00:07:32.118 --> 00:07:33.119  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Listen carefully.</i>

119
00:07:34.220 --> 00:07:36.155  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Evacuate Japan.</i>

120
00:07:37.557 --> 00:07:40.226  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>You run out of time in three days.</i>

121
00:07:41.461 --> 00:07:43.729  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>If the Japanese government</i>
<i>or the U.S. military</i>

122
00:07:44.764 --> 00:07:46.966  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>rejects our demands,</i>

123
00:07:47.066 --> 00:07:49.502  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>then they can come risk their lives</i>
<i>to stop us.</i>

124
00:07:50.069 --> 00:07:53.673  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
