127
00:08:01.981 --> 00:08:06.586  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Even if this country is covered</i>
<i>in a cloud of poison gas...</i>

128
00:08:06.786 --> 00:08:08.988  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>the Ajin alone will survive.</i>

129
00:08:10.857 --> 00:08:11.724  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Move out.

130
00:08:12.658 --> 00:08:16.229  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>We will become the rulers of this country.</i>

131
00:08:19.165 --> 00:08:21.501  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
END TRANSMISSION

132
00:08:23.936 --> 00:08:25.505  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
